snippet.title: Virginia Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Virginia is a single-player first-person thriller set in a small town with a secret. Coming to PS4, Xbox One, PC and Mac September 22nd!

Experience a missing person investigation through the eyes of graduate FBI agent Anne Tarver.

Find out more:
http://virginia.game/
https://twitter.com/VariableState

For behind the scenes details on all of 505's games, head to the official 505 Games Blog: http://www.505games.com/blog
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/505Games
Twitter: https://twitter.com/505_Games
